title: Classmate is Not a Demon - Novel Updates
tags: Beautiful Female Lead   Clever Protagonist   Cold Love Interests   Devoted Love Interests   Female Protagonist   Love Interest Falls in Love First   Modern Day   Power Couple   Time Travel   Unconditional Love
author: 时微月上
description:
Qu Moshang, who was about to get engaged, accidentally discovered that her fiancé was entangled with a woman. The Phoenix man not only had two hearts, but also used her company as a bargaining chip to please the cold-faced beauty. However, the woman backhanded the company’s shares back to her, and Qu Moshang was unexpectedly reborn before she could figure out the direction. . . . It’s just that this cold beauty who isn’t a demon is her junior high school classmate?
+++
Rebirth to the era when the winner of life’s rival was still a devastated little cabbage, and Qu Moshang discovered that this classmate was really not a demon.
Qu Moshang; Come here, I won’t eat you.
Lin Qinghan: Well, I’m sure you won’t eat me.
Qu Moshang: You can eat me though.

Reborn cold bookworm x Soft and sticky counterattacking little bitter gourd>
